<body>
On mouse over here bold words of the following paragraph will be highlighted.
We have just started this section for the users (beginner to intermediate) who want to work with various JavaScript roblems and write scripts online to test their JavaScript skill.

<script>
function greenWords() {
var par = document.getElementsByTagName('P')[1];
var str = par.getElementsByTagName('STRONG');
for(var i = 0; i < str.length; i++) {
str[i].style.color ='green';
}
}
function returnColor() {
var par1 = document.getElementsByTagName('P')[1];
var str1= par1.getElementsByTagName('STRONG');
for(var j = 0; j < str1.length; j++) {
str1[j].style.color ='black';
}
}
</script>	
</body>
